2004年十月，吉布森重新开始创作博客，在创作《幽灵山村》时，时常不按顺序地从小说中节选片段发布在博客上，在创作《零历史》时亦然，只是不如先前频繁。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gibson|first=William|url=http://www.williamgibsonbooks.com/blog/2006_06_01_archive.asp#114922706834176317|title=Moor|date=2006-06-01|access-date=2007-11-04|publisher=WilliamGibsonBooks.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011075515/http://williamgibsonbooks.com/blog/2006_06_01_archive.asp#114922706834176317|archive-date=2007-10-11|url-status=yes}}
